description: Joanne Hayes was wrongly accused after a newborn boy's body was found on a Kerry beach in 1984.
title: Kerry babies: Irish state apologises to Joanne Hayes
title_page: Kerry babies: Irish state apologises to Joanne Hayes - BBC News
maintext: Detectives believed she may have given birth to twins - despite the two babies having different blood groups - and that she had murdered the baby found on the beach now known as Baby John.
